{"tid":2293532,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃店搞大笪地「光復文創界」","createTime":"2020-11-20T09:55:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T09:55:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f1c9f0887311b9024ac9fd7fbb9f3b8b4cc9a82e","tid":2293532,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T09:55:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/EI7IW3NSYJARDAY2KYCQ77TZ7I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2FEI7IW3NSYJARDAY2KYCQ77TZ7I%2F&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6Bdg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=05d8469f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2FEI7IW3NSYJARDAY2KYCQ77TZ7I%2F&h=5536da72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/EI7IW3NSYJARDAY2KYCQ77TZ7I/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n黃店搞大笪地「光復文創界」<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】建制派狙擊黃店，有荔枝角的黃店店長無懼壓力，自組市集將黃色力量發揚光大，聲言勢要光復文創界，以一切從簡慳成本，將老套地攤變成特色市集。<br />\n<br />\n曾於深水埗區一個大型文創商場黃店任店長的的光仔籌辦黃市集「港野」，由同路人平租荔枝角工廈樓上場地和傢俬，並用最少佈置減省成本，「就得呢幅地咁大笪地方，你想點就點」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FGrUjPcYnJhGhG4r0RRKg9ZrL0Q=/720x462/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XI3NJT5LAFCGRMSQMCKASJIH4A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFGrUjPcYnJhGhG4r0RRKg9ZrL0Q%3D%2F720x462%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXI3NJT5LAFCGRMSQMCKASJIH4A.jpg&h=d8cb67ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■市集籌辦人光仔（左）租用荔枝角工廈舉辦黃店市集，更踢走裝飾減低成本。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n擺檔店主親身推介品牌<br />\n<br />\n逾廿檔將於明起一連兩天擺檔，主場地位於荔枝角香港工業中心B座四樓，另於斜對街三樓滙華工廠大廈的樓副場地則設包括「HongKong_IN」等幾家工作室。參與活動人士須事前網上登記（shorturl.at/bhnr3）。<br />\n<br />\n光仔認為租金壓力會令檔攤千篇一律。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n他又自行「fact check」參加的檔主，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n主打手工啤的「黃黚黚」首次擺檔。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n同樣於露天擺檔的「飾簡」店主Christie則是市集常客。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n室內擺檔專賣鸚鵡主題手作工藝品的「桔蕉工作室」。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/s5h_jzBEJNbogljnrjjddbIdT7Y=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VBHNFD4DMZGMHM7MHT5FSUHWZ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fs5h_jzBEJNbogljnrjjddbIdT7Y%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVBHNFD4DMZGMHM7MHT5FSUHWZ4.jpg&h=b74f64a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■光仔直言要將黃色力量發揚光大。"}]}